{"tid":47460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真相曝光！高盛：中國資金外流高達1.1兆美元","createTime":"2016-12-20T11:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T13:24:39.000Z","uid":35519,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"542cd16e6985cd95240aabc903660d85f4a75677","tid":47460,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真相曝光！高盛：中國資金外流高達1.1兆美元</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">鉅亨網編譯張正芊<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.cnyes.com/news/id/3655472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F3655472&d=wLsFwmuB8qaW%2FGzkDIfviUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=a05ba655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.cnyes.com/news/id/3655472</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/3655472/l/84257786dcf39ae9ff58608da3e01b07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F3655472%2Fl%2F84257786dcf39ae9ff58608da3e01b07.jpg&h=72b0cb50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高盛 (Goldman Sachs) 全球投資研究部亞洲區執行董事鄧敏強的團隊周五 (16 日) 警告，自去年 8 月至今年 11 月，中國資金外流的規模其實高達 1.1 兆美元，比人行官方公布的 5400 億美元還高出一倍多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/3655472/m/6987a7af861d448188d2eea57cd8b3d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F3655472%2Fm%2F6987a7af861d448188d2eea57cd8b3d1.jpg&h=99dfa7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>高盛估計近年中國資金外流實際規模。深色塊：近期不尋常跨境人民幣流動；淺色塊：根據外管局在岸外匯結算數據推算的外匯資金流。</em><br />\n<br />\n鄧敏強等人發布報告指出，他們的統計加入了人行旗下中國國家外匯管理局 (SAFE) 的資金流數據，包括被視為獲准的中國企業需求，以及透過離岸人民幣市場流出的資金。鄧表示，今年 6 月以來的數據一再暗示，人行拋售外匯的規模遠大於官方外匯儲備數據所暗示，「平均每個月的差距約 250 億美元」。<br />\n<br />\n高盛指出，單單上個月，淨流出中國的資金規模已達 692 億美元，遠高於 6 月份以來每月平均的 500 億美元左右。SAFE 據顯示，上月透過人民幣支付流出的資金，已由 10 月份的 290 億美元跳上 336 億美元，持續 14 個月失血。<br />\n<br />\n反映人行資產負債表上外匯規模的人行人民幣部位，上個月也暴減 3830 億元人民幣 (550 億美元)，創 1 月以來最大降幅。<br />\n<br />\n光銀國際研究部主管林樵基對《彭博社》表示，今年底至明年第一季，中國資金外流及人民幣貶值將持續甚至惡化，因投資人對美元轉強及中國經濟情況越來越擔憂。他預估人民幣兌美元「非常快」將貶至 7 元，而儘管中國當局近期內將繼續加緊控管資金，但長期而言仍不改推動人民幣國際化。"},{"pid":"dfcc40a4a191448820056c491cbfd23d6b1f5590","tid":47460,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">冇D咁既事</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c33e4b6df6a9eba2ab686428389a513cb2f5a1","tid":47460,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"高盛又做謠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a03ba20120696a24ab0e64dc0fea8df50765a9","tid":47460,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"資金外流 中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8674839b3db2e30ede24d9e8315d78a476541d51","tid":47460,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"12月穿3萬億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d0fa3a026d6244e9294e32f98e1f5e865c28e0","tid":47460,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:11:42.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑<br />\n<br />\n股市冥幣咁樣跌法，支那好大機會撐唔到年底，頂盡出年農曆新年就徹底玩完..."},{"pid":"8b1ef3bd3c8c212603ac26cd2966219d4326cab6","tid":47460,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:13:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國加息引債市大暴跌　支那經濟迎來死期一個月內必將大爆煲</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://sinastorage.com/storage.caitou.sina.com.cn/products/201611/2291585838500a5dc231e14d6f6734c6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsinastorage.com%2Fstorage.caitou.sina.com.cn%2Fproducts%2F201611%2F2291585838500a5dc231e14d6f6734c6.jpeg&h=5db032fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2016-12-16<br />\n<br />\n美國聯準會（FED）示意明年升息次數由 2 次增為 3 次，中國市場又謠言滿天飛，中國債市掀起腥風血雨，5 年期和 10 年期債券期貨重挫，盤中雙雙吃下跌停，創下前所未見的紀錄。 <br />\n<br />\n南華早報報導，15 日早盤，中國債市大暴跌，中國 5 年期和 10 年期債券期貨分別下跌 2%、1.2%，跌停鎖死，為前所未見的情況。重新打開之後，跌幅縮小。與此同時，中國 10 年期公債殖利率也一度暴衝至 3.59%，遠高於 14 日盤中高點的 3.2%。 <br />\n<br />\n長債殖利率跳升，市場間的借貸成本跟著飆漲，各天期的上海銀行間同業拆款利率（Shibor）連三漲，3 個月期的 Shibor 更連續 41 天攀升，來到 3.1635%。隔夜 Shibor 也上升 1.1% 至 2.311%。 <br />\n<br />\n債市恐慌促使人行大幅放水，透過公開市場操作，挹注人民幣 1,450 億元資金，穩定軍心。 <br />\n<br />\n為何中國流動性轉緊？中媒《第一財經日報》15 日報導，同業報價平台 Dealing Matrix 人士告訴《第一財經日報》，市場人士透露，因為債市巨虧，需要資金彌補虧損，多家銀行取消了原定的資金融出計劃。加深資金緊張。 <br />\n<br />\n債市情況不利之際，又有負面傳言滿天飛，更加劇跌勢。 <br />\n<br />\n未來一個月將會是明斯基時刻的觸發期，中國經濟的結構性病症表明，隨着貨幣政策的逐步收緊，資產端的表現越來越差強人意，債務端的壓力越來越嚴峻，明斯基時刻的到來已經是難以避免的。"},{"pid":"3c2261a1968a934c74f7da0eb32ad14686435e25","tid":47460,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"究竟支爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c49e5087f9e22a5e284b2915f63b116d033053","tid":47460,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da7a04d7c8c3d90ae5f59eeb93afc6b9a84a95e","tid":47460,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟支爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前或者係流料，今次珍珠冇咁真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab972d17b82a59c775f5e0bc41d8493ba3ad04f7","tid":47460,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"還有黨"},{"pid":"6059f0d2aaa8d9de4d41cd19d9076a4a92a87157","tid":47460,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟支爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngoldman sachs講得出黎即係未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當佢唱好中國就差唔多係時候"},{"pid":"6c7e41146e272d2c78cfa277801fbceb34a9e7f1","tid":47460,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高盛又做謠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n外部勢力"},{"pid":"8a2477f5d443b96c20e1b92e8ba7c1f98cc4f22f","tid":47460,"uid":41037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ba39b7b9b9200fe8e7e17f2d5a866b49c0458d8","tid":47460,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"你有錢俾 人地都唔會串你啦 忍得你耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7be535387fe8697ec258c0af66fdad264962f0","tid":47460,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟支爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊有咁易呀，有十四億奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd69d15e3328892b5483481d9776a173ce7f550","tid":47460,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟支爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊有咁易呀，有十四億奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但十四億奴隸要對抗毒霧喎，支爆好多野爆，你估得經濟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe3afc5a3c9c6b55f6cb77a2f60b449ddafda08","tid":47460,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"陰司紙都冇呢個銀碼 你贏哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca2eb910550e7ef047492667c299395123122cf","tid":47460,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417eb3175569b13915d4750cbda990f3e201e67b","tid":47460,"uid":6639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"資金外流令中國人更加團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}